      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next owner, this vehicle offers a practical opportunity for someone seeking affordable transportation or a solid project at an accessible price. It shows its age and will benefit from some cosmetic and mechanical attention, but it presents strong value for a buyer who wants maximum car for the money. Priced to sell and well-suited for a handyman, first-time buyer, or anyone looking for a low-cost option.",
