    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of life left for the right person? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a dependable budget-friendly option for someone who wants cheap transportation, a project, or a handy runaround. It has the usual wear you\u2019d expect at this stage, but it still offers great value for the money and could be a smart buy for a buyer who doesn\u2019t mind a little TLC. Priced to sell and worth a look if you want honest, low-cost motoring.",
      "price": 5950.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Clean, honest driver with solid bones and plenty of usable life left. Starts up, runs, and moves out with a strong mechanical feel, with the kind of straightforward, analog character enthusiasts appreciate. Not a perfect cosmetic car, but it presents as a capable budget-friendly ride, commuter, or weekend project with good parts value and real-world utility. A great chance to get into something affordable that still has plenty of potential.",
      "price": 6900.0,
