      "description": "This car has the kind of honest, road-worn charm you notice right away\u2014the sort of machine that still has stories left to tell. It\u2019s an ideal fit for someone who appreciates a practical project, a dependable around-town companion, or a budget-friendly set of wheels with real personality. There\u2019s a rugged, unpolished appeal here that makes it easy to imagine putting it to work, giving it your own touch, and enjoying the value it brings from day one. Priced to move and full of potential for the right buyer.",
      "price": 5900.0,
